The paper focuses on the cyber risks associated with IoT in the Industry 4.0 sector, which falls under the domain of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The study also involves synthesizing findings from literature reviews and comparing cyber security frameworks, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also discusses the economic impact of IoT cyber risk, which could be related to cyber insurance (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
